\pard\keepn\sb100\sa100\b\fs36 6. Contributing\par
\fs28 6.1. Graphics\par
\fs24 6.1.1. Can i make a custom avatar?\par
\pard\b0 Yes. Create an image fulfilling the avatar specifications and drop it to the directory \f1\fs20 graphics/avatar\f0\fs24  for testing. If it looks fine, send it to the author who will include it to the next build of the client. \par
\pard\keepn\sb100\sa100\b 6.1.2. What are specifications for avatar images?\par
\pard\b0 PNG-files 32x32, pure black (R,G,B = 0,0,0) is invisible. The picture must not violate copyrights or good taste. \par
